Package io.shiromi.saml.types

Class GenericType

java.lang.Object
io.shiromi.saml.types.AbstractType<Object>
io.shiromi.saml.types.GenericType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class GenericType extends AbstractType<Object>
Instances of the class GenericType carry a value of type Object, essentially acting as an Any type, as the same suggests, this class' sole purpose is to allow interchangeability between types and generification of types.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Shiromi
